    "body": "found the issue! truffle-contract's `send()` function is bad software and doesn't accept an options hash like every other method in the library, so the sender of that transaction is always the default account, which is not authorized and therefore fails the whitelist check.\r\n\r\nsending a normal transaction is the move. I'll have a PR for this in a few minutes.",
